name: Havee Racing
description:
It's all free.
You like car race with high speed. And of course so funny if you race your car on beach side.
You are military car driver. You have to drive your car to your army camp on time. it's late now, and so you have to run your car fastly, and pick some money on the road to buy weapons. Hey! See how well you execute the task.
That's easy to play, just swing your device and gain score by driving your amy car.
Good luck.
